56		Message number
2 message ~	names
Message_2 from Grock:  FIX FOR STAIRSTEP EFFECT
~
A message from Grock lies here.
~
I think I fixed the stairstep effect, ie the cursor nevers goes back to the
beginning of the line, it only drops DOWN one line.  If you are having this
problem, type:  toggle carriage
then if that doesn't work, try:  toggle cr
If neither of these work, let me know.  For those of you with no problems
currently, I don't think these things will hurt you, but they probably won't
help
either.
Grock

~
